ls%20Fargo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20San%20Francisco-based%20bank%2C%20partnered%20with%20Bilt%20Technologies%2C%20a%20fintech%20startup%2C%20to%20offer%20a%20rewards%20program%20that%20incentivizes%20customers%20to%20pay%20rent%20with%20a%20credit%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20young%20renters%2C%20the%20allure%20was%20clear%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbilt-mastercard-card-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBilt%3C%2Fa%3E%20offered%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-no-fee-credit-card%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ezero-annual-fee%20card%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20allowed%20its%20users%20to%20earn%20a%20point%20for%20every%20dollar%20spent%20on%20rent%20without%20incurring%20transaction%20fees.%20The%20only%20requirement%20was%20that%20customers%20make%20five%20transactions%20each%20statement%20period%20to%20earn%20the%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECustomers%20could%20also%20receive%20points%20for%20travel%20and%20dining.%20Those%20points%20could%20then%20be%20used%20for%20purchases%20with%20any%20of%20Bilt's%20partners%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbilt-adds-alaska-airlines-transfer-partner-loses-american-airlines-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlaska%20Airlines%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Virgin%20Atlantic%2C%20Hyatt%2C%20and%20Soul%20Cycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Ffinance%2Fbanking%2Fwells-fargo-credit-card-rent-rewards-8e380852%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Bilt%20opened%20more%20than%20one%20million%20accounts%20within%20the%20first%2018%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20return%20for%20the%20bank%20has%20yet%20to%20materialize.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2241a0e031-bf66-4b05-bc06-db1e4feed271%5C%22%3EA%20'generation%20of%20young%2C%20affluent%20new%20customers'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBilt's%20demographic%20is%20decidedly%20different%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Faverage-american-net-worth%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaverage%20American%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20who%20has%20a%20median%20salary%20of%20just%20less%20than%20%2460%2C000%2C%20with%2049%25%20of%20them%20holding%20onto%20a%20credit%20card%20balance%20month-to-month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20report%20on%20Bilt%20prepared%20by%20investment%20banking%20firm%20Financial%20Technology%20Partners%20said%20the%20company%20was%20reaching%20out%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bgeneration%20of%20young%2C%20affluent%20new%20customers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20February%20interview%20with%20The%20Wise%20Marketer%2C%20Dave%20Canty%2C%20Bilt's%20head%20of%20loyalty%20and%20partnerships%2C%20said%20the%20company's%20core%20demographics%20are%20between%2024%20and%2034%2C%20with%20a%20median%20age%20of%20about%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20average%20income%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20the%20interview%2C%20%26quot%3Bis%20about%20%24147%2C000%2C%20so%20these%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeet-typical-dink-double-income-no-kid-net-worth-retirement-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh-achieving%20young%20professionals%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBilt%20CEO%20and%20founder%20Ankur%20Jain%20said%20on%20X%20that%20his%20company%20was%20attracting%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20valuable%20customers%26quot%3B%20for%20Wells%20Fargo%20at%20low%20costs.%20The%20average%20customer%20is%2031%20years%20old%20and%20has%20a%20760%20FICO%20score%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKevin%20and%20Amanda%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESmidt%2C%20a%20Miami-based%20couple%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20they've%20been%20Bilt%20cardmembers%20for%20about%20a%20year%20after%20they%20heard%20about%20the%20program%20on%20a%20financial%20podcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20never%20heard%20of%20it%2C%20and%20I%20was%20like%2C%20'Wow%2C%20that's%20so%20smart%2C'%20because%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20if%20you%20live%20in%20a%20major%20city%20like%20New%20York%20or%20Miami%20%E2%80%94%20you're%20spending%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20on%20rent%2C%26quot%3B%20Amanda%2C%20a%2032-year-old%20business%20owner%20and%20registered%20nurse%20anesthetist%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20like%2C%20'This%20makes%20so%20much%20sense%20because%20I%20have%20this%20huge%20payment%20every%20month%2C%20but%20now%20I'll%20get%20points.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20described%20themselves%20as%20financially%20responsible%2C%20telling%20BI%20they%20never%20carry%20a%20balance%20on%20their%20multiple%20personal%20credit%20cards%2C%20including%20Bilt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20heard%20about%20it%20on%20a%20financial%20podcast%20about%20investing.%20I'm%20a%20responsible%20person%20who%20invests%2C%20you%20know%20what%20I%20mean%3F%26quot%3B%20Amanda%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKevin%2C%20who%20is%2033%20and%20working%20on%20his%20fellowship%20as%20an%20orthopedic%20surgeon%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20card%20has%20been%20fruitful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20said%20they%20racked%20up%2056%2C000%20points%20in%20about%20six%20months%20and%20transferred%20them%20through%20one%20of%20Bilt's%20programs%20to%20turn%20their%20earnings%20into%20126%2C000%20points%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvirgin-atlantic-business-class-flight-experience-photos-worth-it-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVirgin%20Atlantic%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Kevin%20said%20they%20used%20the%20reward%20to%20pay%20for%20three%20flights%2C%20two%20in%20business%20class%20and%20one%20on%20Virgin's%20new%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20husband%20told%20BI%20that%20he%20could%20see%20the%20card%20being%20beneficial%20for%20general%20use%2C%20given%20the%20rewards%20a%20customer%20could%20gain%20from%20travel%20and%20dining.%20But%20for%20the%20Smidts%2C%20most%20of%20the%20other%20purchases%20they%20made%20with%20Bilt%20were%20to%20meet%20the%20minimum%20five-transaction%20requirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20the%20times%2C%20that's%20like%20a%20latte%2C%26quot%3B%20Amanda%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20do%20small%20purchases%20to%20be%20able%20to%20get%20the%20points%20from%20the%20rent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKevin%20said%20he%20hopes%20Wells%20Fargo%20doesn't%20get%20rid%20of%20Bilt%2C%20but%20Amanda%20chimed%20in%3A%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20actually%2C%20we%20just%20bought%20a%20house.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOh%20yeah%2C%26quot%3B%20Kevin%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Bso%20we%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20use%20it%20anymore.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2252322de8-1296-4a1c-9556-5d6acb37ec6d%5C%22%3EA%20costly%20program%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Journal%20reported%20on%20Sunday%20that%20Wells%20Fargo%20was%20losing%20up%20to%20%2410%20million%20monthly%20to%20sustain%20the%20Bilt%20program%2C%20citing%20anonymous%20current%20and%20former%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20part%20of%20the%20problem%20is%20that%20Wells%20Fargo%20may%20have%20miscalculated%20how%20Bilt%20customers%20would%20use%20the%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Journal%20reported%20that%20only%2015%25%20to%2025%25%20of%20the%20dollars%20people%20spent%20on%20the%20card%20were%20carried%20over%20month-to-month%2C%20which%20is%20crucial%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efor%20Wells%20Fargo%20to%20generate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcredit-card-interest-rates-late-fees-are-rising-recession-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterest-fee%20revenue%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20bank%20projected%20that%20the%20carry-over%20would%20be%20between%20half%20and%20three-quarters%20of%20the%20dollars%20spent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWells%20Fargo%20also%20anticipated%20that%2065%25%20of%20the%20credit%20card%20purchase%20volume%20would%20be%20for%20expenses%20other%20than%20rent.%20Instead%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F12-million-americans-spend-over-half-paycheck-rent-harvard-study-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20The%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20most%20purchases%20are%20for%20rent%20payments%20despite%20Bilt's%20requirement%20for%20five%20transactions%20per%20statement%20to%20score%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWells%20Fargo%20and%20Bilt%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20reported%20numbers.%20A%20Bilt%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Wells%20Fargo%20does%20not%20make%20the%20numbers%20publicly%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20email%2C%20a%20Wells%20Fargo%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20co-branded%20credit%20cards%20are%20%26quot%3Bone%20modest%20piece%20of%20the%20company's%20overall%20credit%20card%20business%20strategy%2C%20and%20the%20BILT%20credit%20card%20is%20one%20component%20of%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20with%20all%20new%20card%20launches%2C%20it%20takes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchase-sapphire-reserve-is-jpmorgans-gateway-drug-2018-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultiple%20years%20for%20the%20initial%20launch%20to%20pay%20off%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20while%20we%20are%20in%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20our%20partnership%2C%20we%20look%20forward%20to%20continuing%20to%20work%20together%20to%20deliver%20a%20great%20value%20for%20our%20customers%20and%20make%20sure%20it's%20a%20win%20for%20both%20BILT%20and%20Wells%20Fargo%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20The%20Journal%2C%20the%20losses%20have%20pushed%20Wells%20Fargo%20to%20rethink%20its%20partnership%20with%20Bilt%2C%20and%20the%20bank%20won't%20renew%20its%20contract%2C%20which%20is%20set%20to%20expire%20in%202029.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Wells%20Fargo%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20has%20been%20no%20conversation%20among%20decision-makers%20to%20exit%20the%20BILT%20agreement.%20To%20suggest%20otherwise%20is%20false.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Bilt%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20Journal's%20story%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Binaccurate%20representation%20of%20our%20strategic%20partnership%20with%20Wells%20Fargo.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20X%2C%20Bilt%20CEO%20Jain%20did%20not%20address%20the%20reported%20losses%20but%20repeated%20Wells%20Fargo's%20statement%20denying%20the%20bank's%20plan%20to%20end%20the%20partnership%20once%20the%20contract%20expires.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwells-fargo-bilt-partnership-gen-z-millennial-credit-card-holders-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718664550000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666fb727ed9a404d829e35ae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwells-fargo-bilt-partnership-gen-z-millennial-credit-card-holders-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Thanks%20to%20savvy%20millennials%2C%20Wells%20Fargo's%20partnership%20with%20Bilt%20Rewards%20%E2%80%94%20a%20renter-friendly%20credit%20card%20program%20%E2%80%94%20could%20be%20costing%20the%20bank%20millions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwells-fargo-bilt-partnership-gen-z-millennial-credit-card-holders-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Swara%20shares%20pics%20from%20Raabiyaa's%20first%20Bakr-Eid%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718664191000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111068601%2Cimgsize-114758.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fswara-bhasker-shares-love-filled-pictures-from-daughter-raabiyaas-first-bakr-eid-celebration%2Farticleshow%2F111068635.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3