EThe%20steering%20wheel.%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Zhang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20using%20the%20corporate%20steering%20wheel%20design%20like%20those%20found%20on%20other%20SUVs%20in%20Hyundai's%20lineup%2C%20the%20Santa%20Fe%20evokes%20the%20look%20and%20feel%20of%20the%20British%20SUV-brand%20that%20also%20inspired%20its%20exterior%20design.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20front%20of%20the%20driver%20is%20a%20configurable%2012.3-inch%20digital%20instrument%20display.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223953%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20digital%20instrument%20display%20in%20a%202024%20Hyundai%20Santa%20Fe%20XRT%20SUV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667048dc764df161125a55fc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222965%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20digital%20instrument%20display.%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Zhang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20driver%20attention%20alert%20system's%20sensor%20juts%20out%20from%20atop%20the%20steering%20column%20and%20can%20sometimes%20block%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20instrument%20display.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20great%20this%20potentially%20lifesaving%20system%20exists%2C%20but%20in%20everyday%20use%20it's%20finicky.%20If%20you%20drive%20with%20your%20hand%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20wheel%2C%20the%20system%20will%20flash%20warning%20messages%20at%20you%20because%20it%20can't%20see%20your%20face.%20It%20won't%20be%20happy%20until%20you're%20back%20at%2010-and-2%20or%209-and-3%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20shifter%20is%20weird%20but%20oddly%20intuitive.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20steering%20column-mounted%20shifter%20in%20a%202024%20Hyundai%20Santa%20Fe%20SUV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666c81ebed9a404d829dfe26%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Santa%20Fe's%20sh