sole.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666c7894e079049018193ac0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20useful%20storage%20drawer.%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Zhang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20center%20console%20armrest%20opens%20forward%20and%20backward%2C%20allowing%20the%20rear%20cabin%20access%20to%20its%20contents%20as%20well.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELike%20in%20other%20Hyundai%20products%20these%20days%2C%20the%20focal%20point%20of%20the%20front%20dash%20is%20a%2012.3-inch%20touchscreen.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20front%20dash%20and%20center%20console%20of%20a%202024%20Hyundai%20Santa%20Fe%20SUV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666c7f5b764df161125a0ea2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Santa%20Fe's%20infotainment%20screen.%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Zhang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20the%20Palisade%20and%20Tucson%2C%20the%20Santa%20Fe%20boasts%20a%20newer%20version%20of%20the%20Hyundai%20user%20interface.%20The%20system%20was%20fairly%20intuitive%20to%20understand%20and%20looked%20great%2C%20with%20both%20Apple%20CarPlay%20and%20Android%20Auto%20included.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBelow%20the%20infotainment%20screen%20on%20the%20dash%20in%20a%20small%20touchscreen%20for%20the%20climate%20control.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223228%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20touchscreen%20climate%20controls%20on%20a%202024%20Hyundai%20Sante%20Fe%20XRT%20SUV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66705a2de0790490181996a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222421%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETouchscreen%20climate%20controls.%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Zhang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20in%20the%20Palisade%2C%20I%20fou