0of%20the%20house.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226240%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tunnels%20in%20Lynnewood%20Hall.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666c948e764df161125a1d6e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETunnels%20in%20Lynnewood%20Hall.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Leland%20Kent%2F%20Abandoned%20Southeast%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20large%20homes%20built%20during%20the%20Gilded%20Age%20often%20incorporated%20hidden%20passages%2C%20commonly%20referred%20to%20as%20servants'%20tunnels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20tunnels%20served%20a%20dual%20purpose%3A%20not%20only%20did%20they%20ensure%20that%20servants%20could%20perform%20their%20duties%20without%20intruding%20upon%20the%20occupants'%20daily%20lives%2C%20but%20they%20also%20provided%20a%20comfortable%20way%20to%20move%20between%20different%20wings%20of%20the%20house%20during%20the%20frigid%20winter%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUsually%20in%20these%20types%20of%20homes%2C%20the%20staff%20were%20hidden%20from%20view%2C%26quot%3B%20Thome%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20partially%20true%20in%20this%20house%2C%20but%20I%20would%20also%20say%20that%20there%20aren't%20as%20many%20back%20hallways%20and%20secret%20passages%20as%20you%20would%20imagine.%20The%20staff%20were%20a%20bit%20more%20public-facing%20in%20this%20home%2C%20which%20is%20unusual%20for%20the%20time%2C%20and%20has%20a%20lot%20to%20do%20with%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Wideners%20were%20new%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20years%20of%20neglect%2C%20the%20tunnels%20of%20Lynnewood%20Hall%20have%20taken%20on%20an%20eerie%20appearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20tunnels%20are%20pitch%20black%20in%20both%20directions%2C%20and%20when%20you%20shine%20a%20light%20down%20there%2C%20the%20darkness%20seems%20to%20eat%20it%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Kent%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20only%20see%20about%20six%20to%20eight%20feet%20in%20front%20of%20you.%26q