%20can%20be%20hacked%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20Mr%20Musk's%20claim%20that%20%26quot%3Beverything%20can%20be%20hacked%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Chandrasekhar%2C%20who%20headed%20the%20Union%20ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20during%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20second%20tenure%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20he%20is%20factually%20incorrect%20in%20saying%20that%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20calculator%20or%20a%20toaster%20cannot%20be%20hacked.%20Therefore%2C%20there%20is%20a%20limit%20in%20terms%20of%20where%20this%20paradigm%20of%20hacking%20can%20extend%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%20%26quot%3BHe%20(Elon%20Musk)%20is%20factually%20wrong...%20To%20claim%20that%20there%20cannot%20be%20a%20secure%20digital%20product%20in%20the%20world%20is%20to%20then%20say%20that%20every%20Tesla%20car%20can%20be%20hacked%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Musk%20would%20be%20right%20only%20if%20the%20machines%20in%20question%20are%20connected%20like%20phones%20or%20computers%2C%20which%20EVMs%20are%20not%2C%20Mr%20Chandrasekhar%20had%20earlier%20argued.%20%26quot%3BElon%20Musk's%20view%20may%20apply%20to%20the%20US%20and%20other%20places%20-%20where%20they%20use%20regular%20compute%20platforms%20to%20build%20internet-connected%20voting%20machines%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BElon%20Musk%20has%20not%20understood%20what%20the%20Indian%20EVM%20is.%20Indian%20EVMs%20do%20not%20lend%20themselves%20to%20being%20hacked%20because%20they%20are%20precisely%20a%20very%20limited-intelligence%20device%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tesla%20chief%20had%20set%20the%20ball%20rolling%20over%20the%20weekend%20with%20his%20post%20questioning%20the%20reliability%20of%20EVMs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20should%20eliminate%20electronic%20voting%20machines.%20The%20risk%20of%20being%20hacked%20by%20humans%20or%20AI%2C%20while%20small%2C%20is%20still%20too%20high%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20posted%20on%20X%20in%20response%20to%20Independent%20US%20Presidential%20candidate%20Robert%20F%20Kennedy%20Jr's%20post%20on%20reports%20that%20Puerto%20Rico's%20elections%20saw%20voting%20irregularities%20in%20hundreds%20of%20EVMs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Opposition%20used%20the%20post%20to%20support%20its%20reservations%20about%20EVMs%2C%20Mr%20Chandrasekhar%20claimed%20that%20Mr%20Musk's%20comment%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20sweeping%20generalisation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20huge%20sweeping%20generalisation%20statement%20that%20implies%20no%20one%20can%20build%20secure%20digital%20hardware.%20Wrong%2C%26quot%3B%20replied%20the%20former%20minister.%20%26quot%3BNo%20connectivity%2C%20no%20bluetooth%2C%20wifi%2C%20Internet%3B%20there%20is%20no%20way%20in.%20Factory-programmed%20controllers%20that%20cannot%20be%20reprogrammed.%20Electronic%20voting%20machines%20can%20be%20architected%20and%20built%20right%20as%20India%20has%20done.%20We%20would%20be%20happy%20to%20run%20a%20tutorial%2C%20Elon%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20post%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnything%20can%20be%20hacked%2C%26quot%3B%20shot%20back%20Mr%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20amid%20reports%20that%20claimed%20a%20relative%20of%20Ravindra%20Waikar%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20MP%20from%20Mumbai%20North%20West%2C%20was%20using%20a%20phone%20that%20could%20be%20connected%20to%20an%20EVM%2C%20Mr%20Musk's%20comments%20fuelled%20massive%20Opposition%20criticism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress's%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said%20EVMs%20in%20India%20%26quot%3Bare%20a%20'black%20box%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bnobody%20is%20allowed%20to%20scrutinize%20them%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BSerious%20concerns%20are%20being%20raised%20about%20transparency%20in%20our%20electoral%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20risks%20of%20EVM%20tampering%20are%20being%20flagged%20in%20several%20elections%20across%20the%20world%20and%20well-known%20technology%20experts%20are%20flagging%20risks%2C%20the%20BJP%20must%20clear%20the%20air%20on%20why%20they%20are%20bent%20on%20using%20EVMs%2C%26quot%3B%20posted%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajya%20Sabha%20MP%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)%20leader%20Priyanka%20Chaturvedi%20flagged%20the%20reports%20on%20Mumbai%20election.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20fraud%20at%20the%20highest%20level%20and%20yet%20the%20%40ECISVEEP%20continues%20to%20sleep%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalls%20for%20a%20return%20to%20paper%20ballot%20has%20already%20been%20decisively%20turned%20down%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20said%20the%20machines%20offer%20significant%20advantages.%20They%20have%20eliminated%20booth%20capturing%20and%20invalid%20votes%2C%20reduce%20paper%20wastage%20and%C2%A0%20expedite%20the%20counting%20process%20minimizing%20errors%2C%20the%20judges%20have%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718650800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F9uivlvpo_elon-musk-rajeev-chandrasekhar_625x300_16_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fevm-tesla-car-ex-minister-rajeev-chandrasekhar-shreds-elon-musks-evm-comment-5911801%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Union%20Minister%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%2C%20who%20had%20offered%20US%20billionaire%20Elon%20Musk%20a%20%26quot%3Btutorial%26quot%3B%20on%20Indian%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machines%2C%20today%20doubled%20down%20on%20his%20argument%2C%20saying%20going%20by%20the%20Tesla%20chief's%20logic%2C%20%26quot%3Bevery%20Tesla%20car%20can%20be%20hacked%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fevm-tesla-car-ex-minister-rajeev-chandrasekhar-shreds-elon-musks-evm-comment-5911801%22%2C%22