A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Ft071vli_d_625x300_17_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fgary-kirsten-lashes-out-at-pakistan-team-after-t20-world-cup-exit-says-no-unity-in-5909818%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan%20cricket%20team%20had%20a%20disappointing%20outing%20in%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20as%20the%20Babar%20Azam-led%20crashed%20out%20in%20the%20group%20stages%20of%20the%20competition%20with%20losses%20against%20United%20States%20and%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fgary-kirsten-lashes-out-at-pakistan-team-after-t20-world-cup-exit-says-no-unity-in-5909818%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3B'Bharat'%2C%20'India'%20To%20Be%20Used%20Interchangeably%20In%20Textbooks%26quot%3B%3A%20NCERT%20Chief%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBharat%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BIndia%26quot%3B%20will%20be%20used%20interchangeably%20in%20NCERT%20textbooks%20as%20is%20the%20case%20in%20the%20country's%20Constitution%2C%20National%20Council%20of%20Educational%20Research%20and%20Training%20Director%20Dinesh%20Prasad%20Saklani%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20comments%20assume%20significance%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20a%20high-level%20panel%20working%20on%20the%20social%20science%20curriculum%20recommending%20that%20%26quot%3BIndia%26quot%3B%20should%20be%20replaced%20with%20%26quot%3BBharat%26quot%3B%20in%20school%20textbooks%20for%20all%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interaction%20with%20PTI%20editors%20at%20the%20agency's%20headquarters%20here%2C%20the%20NCERT%20chief%20said%20both%20the%20words%20will%20be%20used%20in%20the%20books%20and%20the%20council%20has%20no%20aversion%20to%20either%20%26quot%3BBharat%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BIndia%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20interchangeable....our%20position%20is%20what%20our%20Constitution%20says%20and%20we%20uphold%20that.%20We%20can%20use%20Bharat%2C%20we%20can%20use%20India%2C%20what%20is%20the%20problem%3F%20We%20are%20not%20in%20that%20debate.%20Wherever%20it%20suits%20we%20will%20use%20India%2C%20wherever%20it%20suits%20we%20will%20use%20Bharat.%20We%20have%20no%20aversion%20to%20either%20India%20or%20Bharat%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20see%20both%20being%20used%20in%20our%20textbooks%20already%20and%20that%20will%20continue%20in%20new%20textbooks.%20This%20is%20a%20useless%20debate%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Saklani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20high-level%20committee%20for%20social%20sciences%2C%20constituted%20by%20the%20NCERT%20to%20revise%20the%20school%20curriculum%2C%20had%20last%20year%20recommended%20that%20%26quot%3BIndia%26quot%3B%20should%20be%20replaced%20with%20%26quot%3BBharat%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20textbooks%20for%20all%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommittee%20chairperson%20CI%20Isaac%2C%20who%20was%20heading%20the%20panel%2C%20had%20said%20they%20have%20suggested%20replacing%20the%20name%20%26quot%3BIndia%26quot%3B%20with%20%26quot%3BBharat%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20textbooks%2C%20introducing%20%26quot%3Bclassical%20history%26quot%3B%2C%20instead%20of%20%26quot%3Bancient%20history%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20curriculum%2C%20and%20including%20the%20Indian%20Knowledge%20System%20(IKS)%20in%20the%20syllabus%20for%20all%20subjects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20committee%20has%20unanimously%20recommended%20that%20the%20name%20Bharat%20should%20be%20used%20in%20the%20textbooks%20for%20students%20across%20classes.%20Bharat%20is%20an%20age-old%20name.%20The%20name%20Bharat%20has%20been%20used%20in%20ancient%20texts%2C%20such%20as%20Vishnu%20Purana%2C%20which%20is%207%2C000%20years%20old%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Isaac%20had%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCERT%20had%20then%20said%20that%20no%20decision%20has%20been%20taken%20on%20panel's%20recommendations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20name%20Bharat%20first%20appeared%20officially%20last%20year%20when%20the%20government%20sent%20out%20G20%20invites%20in%20the%20name%20of%20%26quot%3BPresident%20of%20Bharat%26quot%3B%2C%20instead%20of%20%26quot%3BPresident%20of%20India%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20the%20nameplate%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20during%20the%20summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%20also%20read%20%26quot%3BBharat%26quot%3B%2C%20instead%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCERT%20is%20once%20again%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20controversy%20with%20the%20revised%20Class%2012%20political%20science%20textbook%20not%20mentioning%20the%20Babri%20masjid%20but%20referring%20to%20it%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bthree-domed%20structure%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718641380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-12%2F191h1oi4_book-generic_625x300_06_December_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbharat-india-to-be-used-interchangeably-in-textbooks-ncert-chief-5911004%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BBharat%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BIndia%26quot%3B%20will%20be%20used%20interchangeably%20in%20NCERT%20textbooks%20as%20is%20the%20case%20in%20the%20country's%20Constitution%2C%20National%20Council%20of%20Educational%20Research%20and%20Training%20Director%20Dinesh%20Prasad%20Saklani%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbharat-india-to-be-used-interchangeably-in-textbooks-ncert-chief-5911004%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbharat-india-to-be-used-interchangeably-in-textbooks-ncert-chief-5911004%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbharat-india-to-be-used