banon-a-funeral-for-two-women-shows-how-furious-fighting-is-ratcheting-up-the-risk-of-all-out-war-13154509%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Won't%20Do%20Any%20Work%20Of%20Muslims%2C%20Yadavs%3A%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20Party%20MP%20Sparks%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20newly%20elected%20MP%20of%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20JD(U)%20on%20Monday%20found%20himself%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20controversy%20for%20laments%20about%20%26quot%3BMuslims%20and%20Yadavs%26quot%3B%20not%20voting%20for%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20clip%20that%20has%20gone%20viral%20on%20social%20media%2C%20Sitamarhi%20MP%20Devesh%20Chandra%20Thakur%20can%20also%20be%20heard%20ruing%20that%20%26quot%3BNDA's%20own%20voters%26quot%3B%20gravitated%20towards%20the%20opposition%20RJD.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thakur%2C%2071%2C%20a%20former%20chairman%20of%20the%20state%20legislative%20council%2C%20made%20his%20parliamentary%20debut%20in%20the%20recently%20held%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20winning%20the%20seat%20by%20a%20modest%20margin%20of%20less%20than%2055%2C000%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20did%20not%20get%20votes%20of%20Suris%20(a%20fishing%20community)%20and%20Kalwars.%20Even%20the%20Kushwahas%20deserted%20me.%20Just%20because%20respected%20Lalu%20Prasad%20(RJD%20supremo)%20gave%20tickets%20to%20many%20Kushwahas.%20Could%20a%20Kushwaha%20elected%20from%20elsewhere%20be%20of%20any%20help%20to%20members%20of%20the%20community%20in%20my%20constituency%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Thakur%20could%20be%20heard%20asking%20in%20the%20video%2C%20which%20was%20not%20independently%20verified%20by%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20Yadavs%20and%20Muslims%20must%20not%20expect%20me%20to%20be%20of%20any%20help%20to%20them.%20They%20will%20be%20treated%20with%20due%20respect%2C%20even%20offered%20tea%20and%20snacks%2C%20when%20they%20call%20on%20me.%20But%20I%20will%20not%20take%20up%20any%20of%20their%20problems.%26quot%3B%20The%20JD(U)%20MP%20added%20that%20he%20had%20expressed%20the%20sentiment%20before%20a%20%26quot%3BMuslim%26quot%3B%20who%20visited%20him%20after%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20asked%20the%20Muslim%20brother%20how%20can%20you%20expect%20me%20to%20work%20for%20you%20when%20you%20did%20not%20vote%20for%20me%20just%20because%20my%20party%20is%20aligned%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Thakur%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20visitor%20agreed%20with%20the%20contention%20and%20went%20back%20feeling%20regret%20for%20his%20electoral%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOften%20called%20%26quot%3BAjaatshatru%26quot%3B%20in%20political%20circles%20because%20of%20his%20friendly%20disposition%2C%20Mr%20Thakur%20retained%20the%20seat%20for%20his%20party%20which%20chose%20to%20drop%20sitting%20MP%20Sunil%20Kumar%20Pintu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thakur%20defeated%20his%20nearest%20RJD%20rival%20Arjun%20Roy%2C%20who%20is%20a%20former%20MP%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JD(U)%20leader's%20outbursts%20met%20with%20disapproval%20from%20the%20RJD%20as%20well%20as%20ally%20BJP%2C%20leaving%20the%20party%20to%20fend%20for%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20remarks%20made%20by%20Mr%20Thakur%20are%20objectionable.%20An%20MP%20is%20the%20representative%20of%20all%20sections%20of%20society%20in%20his%20constituency%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bhai%20Virendra%2C%20the%20RJD's%20chief%20spokesperson%20and%20an%20MLA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20OBC%20Morcha%20national%20general%20secretary%20Nikhil%20Anand%20also%20came%20out%20with%20a%20strongly%20worded%20statement%2C%20but%20without%20mentioning%20Mr%20Thakur%20by%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiving%20vent%20to%20frustration%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20smacks%20of%20caste%20prejudice%20is%20shameful%20and%20deplorable%20in%20politics.%20The%20BJP%20takes%20all%20social%20segments%20along.%20In%20Bihar%2C%20no%20political%20party%20can%20succeed%20if%20it%20tries%20to%20marginalise%20Yadavs%2C%20who%20are%2014%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20population%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Anand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leader%20underscored%20%26quot%3B27%20OBCs%2C%20four%20of%20them%20Yadavs%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Union%20Council%20of%20Ministers%20and%20claimed%20that%20it%20was%20proof%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20commitment%20to%20%26quot%3Bsocial%20harmony%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJD(U)%20chief%20spokesman%20and%20MLC%20Neeraj%20Kumar%20responded%20to%20the%20criticisms%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20unthinkable%20that%20Thakur%20will%20discriminate%20against%20any%20section%20of%20society.%20He%20was%20just%20expressing%20his%20pain%20at%20not%20getting%20votes%20of%20even%20those%20whom%20he%20may%20have%20helped%20him%20personally%20but%20who%20got%20swayed%20by%20other%20considerations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718639940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fh5i68na8_devesh-thakur_625x300_17_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwont-do-any-work-of-muslims-yadavs-nitish-kumars-party-mp-sparks-row-devesh-chandra-thakur-5910333%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20newly%20elected%20MP%20of%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20JD(U)%20on%20Monday%20found%20himself%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20controversy%20for%20laments%20about%20%26quot%3BMuslims%20and%20Yadavs%26quot%3B%20not%20voting%20for%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwont-do-any-work-of-muslims-yadavs-nitish-kumars-party-mp-sparks-row-devesh-chandra-thakur-5910333%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2