ut%20contesting%20and%20that%20she%20would%20give%20Wayanad%20her%20%26quot%3Bbest%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20very%20happy%20to%20be%20able%20to%20represent%20the%20people%20of%20Wayanad%20and%20all%20I'll%20say%20is%20that%20I%20won't%20let%20them%20feel%20his%20(Rahul%20Gandhi's)%20absence.%20He%20said%20he%20will%20come%20frequently%2C%20but%20I%20will%20work%20just%20as%20hard%20and%20try%20to%20make%20everyone%20happy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20family%20bastion%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Amethi%2C%20is%20already%20back%20in%20Congress%20hands%2C%20with%20long-time%20Gandhi%20family%20aide%20KL%20Sharma%20besting%20the%20BJP's%20former%20Union%20minister%20Smriti%20Irani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20decided%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20will%20retain%20Raebareli%20because%20it%20is%20close%20to%20his%20heart%20and%20the%20people%20have%20been%20with%20the%20family%20for%20generations%2C%26quot%3B%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said%20after%20a%20meeting%20this%20evening%20to%20deliberate%20on%20this%20and%20other%20issues.%20The%20assent%20of%20Kerala%20Congress%20was%20conveyed%20by%20the%20presence%20of%20KC%20Venugopal%2C%20who%20stood%20shoulder%20to%20shoulder%20with%20Mr%20Kharge%20at%20the%20post-meet%20press%20conference%20at%20Mr%20Kharge's%20residence.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThanking%20the%20people%20of%20Wayanad%20for%20their%20%26quot%3Blove%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20told%20them%20that%20they%20will%20now%20have%20%26quot%3Btwo%20members%20of%20parliament%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20it%20a%20'tough%20decision%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BPriyanka%20will%20contest%20from%20Wayanad%2C%20but%20I%20will%20be%20a%20frequent%20visitor%20and%20we%20will%20meet%20the%20promises%20made%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Wayanad%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20electoral%20debut%20of%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20has%20been%20speculated%20on%20since%20at%20least%202019%2C%20when%20many%20in%20the%20Congress%20expected%20her%20to%20lead%20the%20battle%20against%20the%20BJP%20by%20contesting%20from%20Varanasi%2C%20the%20constituency%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20But%20the%20party%20was%20kept%20waiting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20recently%20concluded%20general%20election%2C%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20had%20again%20turned%20down%20requests%20to%20contest%20%E2%80%93%20the%20plan%20was%20to%20have%20the%20siblings%20contest%20from%20Amethi%20and%20Raebareli.%20But%20the%20fielding%20of%20KL%20Sharma%2C%20who%20was%20intimately%20acquainted%20with%20both%20constituencies%20for%20decades%2C%20from%20Amethi%20paid%20off%20in%20spades%2C%20with%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20loyalist%20beating%20the%20BJP's%20former%20Union%20minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20by%201.6%20lakh%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20had%20told%20party%20leaders%20in%20private%20that%20she%20had%20reservations%20about%20all%20three%20Gandhis%20being%20in%20parliament.%20She%20was%20concerned%20that%20it%20would%20only%20provide%20ammunition%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20strengthen%20their%20%26quot%3Bdynastic%20politics%26quot%3B%20allegation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718636340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F0u6mrp9_rahul-gandhi-priyanka-gandhi-rahul-priyanka_625x300_13_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fi-am-not-nervous-priyanka-gandhi-to-make-poll-debut-from-wayanad-5910123%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20long-awaited%20electoral%20debut%20of%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20will%20happen%20from%20Kerala's%20Wayanad%2C%20the%20seat%20that%20will%20shortly%20be%20vacated%20by%20her%20brother%2C%20Congress's%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fi-am-not-nervous-priyanka-gandhi-to-make-poll-debut-from-wayanad-5910123%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Priyanka%20Gandhi%20To%20Contest%20from%20Wayanad%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20Keeps%20Raebareli%20Seat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMaking%20two%20major%20announcements%2C%20the%20Congress%20on%20Monday%20said%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20decided%20to%20give%20up%20the%20Wayanad%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%20Kerala%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20family%20bastion%20of%20Raebareli%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%2C%20capping%20years%20of%20speculation%2C%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20is%20finally%20making%20her%20electoral%20debut%20from%20the%20constituency%20he%20is%20vacating.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnnouncing%20the%20decisions%20after%20a%20high-level%20Congress%20meeting%2C%20party%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20who%20was%20flanked%20by%20the%20Gandhi%20siblings%2C%20said%20the%20call%20on%20which%20constituency%20to%20vacate%20was%20taken%20now%20as%20the%20last%20day%20for%20doing%20so%20is%20Tuesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20party%20has%20decided%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20should%20keep%20the%20Raebareli%20seat%20because%20it%20has%20been%20close%20to%20him%20and%20his%20family%20for%20generations.%20The%20people%20of%20the%20constituency%20and%20people%20in%20the%20Congress%20feel%20this%20will%20be%20good%20for%20the%20party%20as%20well.%20More%20importantly%2C%20he%20has%20received%20love%20from%20the%20people%20of%20Wayanad%20and%20people%20there%20want%20him%20to%20retain%20the%20seat.%20But%20the%20rules%20don't%20allow%20this.%20So%20we%20have%20decided%20that%20Priyanka%20ji%20will%20contest%20from%20Wayanad%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20Hindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPriyanka%20Gandhi%20had%20said%20%3Cem%3E'ladki%20hoon%2C%20lad%20sakti%20hoon'%3C%2Fem%3E%20(I%20am%20a%20girl%2C%20I%20can%20fight)%20and%20this%20%3Cem%3Eladki%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecan%20fight%20from%20there%20(Wayanad)%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20to%20laughter%20as%20he%20went%20on%20to%20thank%20Ms%20Gandhi%20for%20the%20Congress'%20success%20in%20Amethi%2C%20Raebareli%20and%20other%20constituencies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20reporter%20asked%20about%20Mr%20Kharge's%20earlier%20claim%2C%20made%20in%20jest%2C%20that%20he%20would%20initiate%20disciplinary%20action%20if%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20did%20not%20follow%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee's%20decision%2C%20the%20party%20president%20sought%20to%20deflect%20but%20Mr%20Gandhi%20chimed%20in%20with%20%26quot%3Ba%20threat%20has%20been%20given%26quot%3B%2C%20eliciting%20more%20laughter.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Tough%20Decision'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20said%20he%20has%20an%20emotional%20connection%20with%20both%20Raebareli%20and%20Wayanad%20and%20expressed%20his%20gratitude%20for%20the%20love%20has%20got%20from%20the%20people%20in%20the%20Kerala%20constituency%20while%20he%20was%20a%20Member%20of%20Parliament%20from%20there%20the%20past%20five%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPriyanka%20will%20contest%20from%20Wayanad%2C%20but%20I%20will%20also%20go%20there%20frequently%20and%20we%20will%20fulfil%20all%20the%20promises%20we%20made%20to%20the%20people%20there.%20I%20have%20an%20old%20connection%20with%20Raebareli%20and%20I%20am%20happy%20to%20represent%20them%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20an%20easy%20decision.%20It%20was%20a%20tough%20one.%20The%20people%20of%20Wayanad%20stood%20with%20me%20and%20supported%20me.%20They%20gave%20me%20energy%20to%20fight%20in%20a%20very%20difficult%20time.%20I%20will%20be%20available%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Wayanad%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20confident%20she%20(Priyanka)%20will%20win%20the%20election%20and%20she%20will%20be%20a%20very%20good%20representative.%20The%20people%20of%20Wayanad%20can%20think%20about%20it%20like%20this%3A%20They%20now%20have%20two%20MPs%2C%20one%20is%20my%20sister%20and%20the%20other%20is%20me.%20My%20doors%20are%20always%20open%20to%20you%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20life%20and%20I%20love%20every%20person%20in%20Wayanad%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Both%20Constituencies%20Getting%20Two%20MPs'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Ms%20Gandhi%20was%20asked%20for%20a%20reaction%2C%20she%20said%20she%20was%20very%20happy%20and%20would%20not%20let%20the%20people%20of%20Wayanad%20feel%20her%20brother's%20absence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20he%20said%2C%20he%20will%20come%20many%20times%20with%20me.%20But%20I%20will%20work%20as%20hard%20and%20try%20to%20be%20a%20good%20representative.%20I%20have%20a%20very%20old%20connection%20with%20Raebareli%20and%20I%20have%20worked%20there%20for%2020%20years.%20That%20connection%20cannot%20break.%20I%20will%20help%20bhaiyya%20(big%20brother)%20in%20Raebareli%20and%20we%20will%20be%20available%20in%20both%20constituencies%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20interjected%20and%20said%20both%20constituencies%20are%20getting%20two%20MPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20she%20was%20nervous%2C%20Ms%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNot%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Raebareli%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20had%20won%20in%20Wayanad%20in%202019%20despite%20suffering%20a%20shock%20defeat%20to%20Smriti%20Irani%20in%20his%20bastion%20of%20Amethi.%20In%20the%20just-concluded%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20he%20won%20again%20in%20Wayanad%20by%20a%20margin%20of%203.64%20lakh%20votes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20eclipsed%20by%20his%20performance%20in%20Raebareli%20-%20helped%20by%20Sonia%20Gandhi's%20emotional%20appeal%20to%20voters%20that%20she%20was%20handing%20her%20son%20to%20them%20-%20which%20he%20won%20with%20a%20margin%20of%203.9%20lakh%20votes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Raebareli%20seat%20was%20held%20by%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20since%202004%20until%20she%20moved%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20earlier%20this%20year.%20Cementing%20its%20status%20as%20a%20Gandhi%20family%20bastion%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20was%20also%20represented%20by%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20grandmother%20and%20former%20PM%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20and%20her%20husband%20Feroze%20Gandhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20was%20not%20inclined%20to%20give%20up%20Wayanad%2C%20what%20also%20worked%20in%20favour%20of%20Raebareli%20was%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20is%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20home%20to%20the%20largest%20number%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20country%2C%20Congress%20sources%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20astounding%20performance%20of%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party-Congress%20alliance%20in%20the%20state%2C%20where%20it%20won%2043%20of%2080%20constituencies%20-%20reducing%20the%20BJP%20from%2062%20to%2033%20-%20also%20played%20a%20role%20in%20the%20decision-making.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPriyanka%20Gandhi's%20Debut%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'will%20she-won't%20she'%20around%20Ms%20Gandhi%20contesting%20elections%20has%20been%20around%20since%20at%20least%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20when%20it%20had%20been%20speculated%20that%20she%20could%20challenge%20PM%20Modi%20in%20the%20Varanasi%20constituency%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Congress%20was%20struggling%20to%20halt%20the%20BJP%20juggernaut.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%20didn't%20happen%2C%20Ms%20Gandhi%20herself%20had%20said%20she%20wasn't%20ruling%20out%20contesting%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20elections%20in%202022%2C%20when%20she%20was%20the%20Congress%20General%20Secretary%20for%20the%20state.%20She%20had%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20hinted%20that%20she%20could%20be%20the%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate%2C%20only%20to%20say%20hours%20later%20that%20she%20had%20meant%20it%20in%20a%20tongue-in-cheek%20way.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%202024%20elections%2C%20the%20speculation%20was%20almost%20seen%20as%20a%20certainty.%20It%20was%20being%20reported%20that%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20would%20contest%20from%20Raebareli%20and%20her%20brother%20would%20fight%20to%20win%20back%20Amethi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20had%20said%20Congress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20had%20asked%20the%20Gandhi%20siblings%20to%20take%20a%20decision%2C%20but%20had%20let%20it%20be%20known%20that%20he%20would%20like%20both%20to%20contest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gandhi%2C%20had%2C%20however%2C%20chosen%20not%20to.%20Sources%20close%20to%20her%20had%20said%20that%20she%20did%20not%20want%20to%20give%20the%20BJP%20a%20reason%20to%20hurl%20allegations%20of%20dynastic%20politics%20at%20the%20Congress%20given%20that%20her%20brother%20and%20mother%20were%20already%20members%20of%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718636280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F1nepanp_rahul-priyanka-1200_625x300_17_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-to-keep-raebareli-seat-in-up-priyanka-gandhi-to-contest-from-wayanad-5910054%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Making%20two%20major%20announcements%2C%20the%20Congress%20on%20Monday%20said%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20decided%20keep%20the%20Raebareli%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%2C%20capping%20years%20of%20speculation%2C%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20is%20finally%20making%20her%20electoral%20debut.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-to-keep-raebareli-seat-in-up-priyanka-gandhi-to-contest-from-wayanad-5910054%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-to-keep-raebareli-seat-in-up-priyanka-gandhi-to-contest-from-wayanad-5910054%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-to-keep-raebareli-seat-in-up-priyanka-gandhi-to-contest-from-wayanad-5910054%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ratna%20on%20her%20bonding%20with%20Anupam%2C%20Paresh%2