20Football%20Federation%20(AIFF)%20has%20decided%20to%20sack%20Indian%20football%20team%20head%20coach%20Igor%20Stimac%20after%20the%20national%20side%20failed%20to%20qualify%20for%20Round%203%20of%20the%20FIFA%20World%20Cup%202026%20qualifiers.%20India%20were%20defeated%202-1%20in%20their%20last%20match%20against%20Qatar%20-%20a%20result%20that%20meant%20the%20national%20side%20finished%20third%20in%20their%20group%20which%20also%20had%20Kuwait%20and%20Afghanistan.%20The%20decision%20came%20just%20weeks%20after%20Sunil%20Chhetri%20retired%20from%20international%20football%20after%20playing%20his%20final%20game%20against%20Kuwait.%20According%20to%20AIFF%20press%20release%2C%20the%20decision%20was%20taken%20after%20senior%20officials%20held%20a%20virtual%20meeting%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20meeting%20was%20chaired%20by%20AIFF%20Vice%20President%20Mr.%20NA%20Haris%20and%20the%20others%20in%20attendance%20were%20Mr.%20Menla%20Ethenpa%20(Member%2C%20Executive%20Committee%20and%20Chairperson%2C%20Finance%20Committee)%2C%20Mr.%20Anilkumar%20Prabhakaran%20(Member%2C%20Executive%20Committee%20and%20Chairperson%2C%20Competitions%20Committee)%2C%20Mr.%20IM%20Vijayan%2C%20(Chairman%20of%20the%20AIFF%20Technical%20Committee)%2C%20Mr.%20Climax%20Lawrence%20(Member%20of%20the%20AIFF%20Technical%20Committee)%20and%20Mr.%20M.%20Satyanarayan%20(Acting%20Secretary%20General)%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNoting%20the%20disappointing%20outcome%20of%20the%20Senior%20Men's%20National%20Team's%20FIFA%20World%20Cup%202026%20qualification%20campaign%2C%20the%20members%20unanimously%20agreed%20that%20a%20new%20Head%20Coach%20would%20be%20best%20placed%20to%20take%20the%20team%20forward.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20meeting%20instructed%20the%20Acting%20Secretary%20General%20Mr.%20Satyanarayan%20to%20notify%20the%20current%20Head%20Coach%20Mr.%20Igor%20Stimac%20of%20its%20decision%20to%20terminate%20his%20engagement.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPursuant%20to%20the%20above%2C%20a%20notice%20of%20termination%20has%20been%20issued%20to%20Mr.%20Stimac%20by%20the%20AIFF%20Secretariat%2C%20and%20he%20stands%20relieved%20of%20his%20obligations%20with%20immediate%20effect.%20The%20AIFF%20thanks%20Mr.%20Stimac%20for%20his%20service%20to%20the%20National%20Team%20and%20wishes%20him%20well%20in%20his%20future%20endeavours%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20lost%20their%20game%20against%20Qatar%202-1%20but%20the%20match%20was%20not%20without%20its%20fair%20share%20of%20controversies.%20Qatar's%20equaliser%20came%20under%20the%20scanner%20when%20replays%20showed%20clearly%20that%20the%20ball%20crossed%20the%20line%20behind%20the%20goal%20before%20it%20was%20played%20back%20to%20the%20attacker%20who%20scored%20the%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718634600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fdljnsbs_igor-stimac-afp_625x300_12_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Figor-stimac-indian-football-coach-sacked-aiff-unhappy-with-him-for-this-reason-5910250%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20All%20India%20Football%20Federation%20(AIFF)%20has%20decided%20to%20sack%20Indian%20football%20team%20head%20coach%20Igor%20Stimac%20after%20the%20national%20side%20failed%20to%20qualify%20for%20Round%203%20of%20the%20FIFA%20World%20Cup%202026%20qualifiers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Figor-stimac-indian-football-coach-sacked-aiff-unhappy-with-him-for-this-reason-5910250%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Figor-stimac-indian-football-coach-sacked-aiff-unhappy-with-him-for-this-reason-5910250%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Figor-stimac-indian-football-coach-sacked-aiff-unhappy-with-him-for-this-reason