uisitive%2C%20loving%20child%2C%20they%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESeeing%20life%20in%20a%20new%20light%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20a%20parent%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20most%20rewarding%20experiences%2C%20shares%20Srivatsan.%20Sendhan%20came%20to%20them%20when%20he%20was%20five%20and%20took%20some%20time%20to%20adjust%20to%20the%20new%20environment.%20He%20was%20also%20one%20of%20the%20only%20brown%20children%20in%20a%20predominantly%20white%20neighbourhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsri2-1718194181-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Srivatsan%20and%20Saravanan%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsri2-1718194181-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsri2-1718194181-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsri2-1718194181-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsri2-1718194181-1152x1536.jpeg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsri2-1718194181-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsri2-1718194181-150x200.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsri2-1718194181.jpeg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352844%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESrivatsan%20and%20Saravanan%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20took%20some%20time%20to%20adjust%20as%20everyone%20around%20him%20spoke%20a%20different%20language%2C%20had%20different%20food%20habits%2C%20and%20a%20different%20skin%20tone.%20The%20journey%20was%20bumpy%20and%20we%20helped%20him%20by%20taking%20him%20on%20playdates%20and%20explaining%20that%20we%20all%20come%20from%20diverse%20backgrounds%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Srivatsan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20this%20small%20human%20run%20around%20the%20house%20asking%20questions%20was%20fun%20for%20the%20new%20parents.%20They%20were%20also%20clear%20about%20explaining%20their%20sexuality%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20Sendhan%20was%20adopted%20by%20them.%20In%20a%20few%20months%2C%20he%20became%20comfortable%20in%20the%20new%20country%20and%20also%20with%20his%20%E2%80%98papa%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98daddy%E2%80%99%2C%20as%20he%20calls%20his%20fathers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20messed%20up%20so%20many%20times%20but%20that%E2%80%99s%20one%20of%20the%20most%20beautiful%20things%20about%20being%20a%20parent.%20We%20are%20learning%20alongside%20our%20son.%20To%20be%20able%20to%20see%20the%20world%20through%20my%20son%E2%80%99s%20eyes%20is%20a%20privilege%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2045-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parents%20enjoy%20taking%20a%20breather%20from%20their%20work%20to%20sit%20and%20play%20with%20crayons%20and%20legos%20and%20watch%20the%20world%20slow%20down%20as%20they%20immerse%20themselves%20into%20a%20six-year-old%E2%80%99s%20world.%20%E2%80%9CHow%20amazing%20and%20simple%20is%20the%20life%20of%20a%20child!%20All%20he%20cares%20about%20is%20playing%2C%20chasing%20butterflies%20and%20building%20sand%20castles%20at%20the%20beach.%20Being%20a%20parent%20is%20truly%20one%20of%20the%20most%20fantastic%20things%20in%20the%20world.%20I%E2%80%99m%20glad%20I%20got%20this%20opportunity%20and%20I%20am%20very%20happy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20also%20certain%20that%20his%20son%20will%20be%20raised%20gently%20and%20provided%20space%20to%20be%20who%20he%20is%20and%20not%20be%20pressured%20to%20conform%20to%20societal%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20n