are%20combined%20and%20transferred%20to%20the%20grow%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20grow%20bag%20is%20designed%20so%20that%20the%20mixture%20does%20not%20come%20into%20direct%20contact%20with%20the%20soil%20beneath%2C%20effectively%20preventing%20bacterial%20and%20fungal%20infections%20from%20spreading.%20Eyyo%20shares%20that%20this%20grow%20bag%20is%20patented%20and%20much%20more%20durable%20than%20standard%20ones%2C%20lasting%20at%20least%20six%20to%20seven%20years%2C%20and%20potentially%20even%20longer%20when%20used%20in%20home%20gardens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20bag%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%20100.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20461px)%20100vw%2C%20461px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-4-1718112692-461x1024.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22461%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20grow%20bags%20use%20a%20clever%20method%20of%20drip%20irrigation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-4-1718112692-461x1024.jpeg%20461w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-4-1718112692-135x300.jpeg%20135w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-4-1718112692-150x333.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-4-1718112692.jpeg%20576w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352684%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20grow%20bags%20use%20a%20clever%20method%20of%20drip%20irrigation.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20these%20grow%20bags%2C%20Eyyo%20has%20developed%20a%20UV%20sheet%20that%20can%20protect%20crops%20from%20harsh%20weather%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20being%20an%20innovative%20farmer%2C%20Eyyo%20is%20a%20generous%20teacher%20who%20loves%20to%20share%20his%20knowledge.%20Although%20he%20has%20reduced%20his%20farming%20activities%20with%20age%2C%20he%20is%20always%20happy%20to%20host%20visitors%20and%20provide%20tips%20on%20organic%20farming.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20very%20important%20to%20consume%20organic%20food.%20Be%20mindful%20of%20what%20you%E2%80%99re%20eating%3B%20try%20to%20grow%20some%20basic%20vegetables%20at%20home.%20Use%20neem%20as%20a%20fertiliser%20for%20your%20kitchen%20garden%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20concludes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20Courtesy%20Eyyo%20Kuriakose%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718115897000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-2-min-1718113039.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D352674%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%2078%2C%20Eyyo%20Kuriakose%20from%20Kottayam%2C%20Kerala%2C%20has%20developed%20a%20patented%2C%20durable%20grow%20bag%20with%20an%20integrated%20drip%20irrigation%20system%2C%20which%20he%20claims%20reduces%20water%20usage%20and%20enhances%20crop%20health.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F352674%2Fgrow-bags-growing-vegetables-eyyo-kuriakose-kottayam-kerala-organic-farming-drip-irrigation%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Engineers%20Design%20100%25%20Solar%20EV%20Tricycle%20For%20Goods%20%26amp%3B%20Waste%20Transport%3B%20Can%20Carry%20Up%20to%20300%20Kg%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20June%2C%20check%20out%20our%20%23ApnaGharSolar%20series%2C%20an%20exclusive%20deep%20dive%20by%20The%20Better%20India%20in%20collaboration%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.solarsquare.in%2F%3Futm_source%3Dsocialmedia%26utm_medium%3Dad%26utm_campaign%3DTheBetterIndia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESolarSquare%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20