ener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F58595%2Fclimate-change-sundarbans-women-photographers-future-health-systems%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esome%20livelihood%20support%3C%2Fa%3E%20we%20would%20be%20able%20to%20encourage%20more%20women%20to%20become%20eco-warriors%20and%20help%20save%20the%20ecologically%20fragile%20Sundarbans%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Biswas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EAll%20pictures%20are%20sourced%20by%20the%20author.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717772153000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWomen-preparing-nursery-bags_11zon-1717769908.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D352436%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Akul%20Biswas%20started%20planting%20mangrove%20saplings%20along%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20Bidyadhari%20river%20in%202005.%20Locals%20took%20notice%20of%20his%20work%20and%20joined%20his%20mission.%20Today%2C%20Biswas%20and%20over%20200%20women%20have%20formed%20the%20Jharkhali%20Sabuj%20Bahini%20that%20works%20towards%20revival%20of%20mangroves%20in%20the%20Sundarbans.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Hiren%20Kumar%20Bose%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F352436%2Fmangrove-plantation-sundarbans-afforestation-conservation-south-parganas-west-bengal-cyclone-blind-activist%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Brothers%E2%80%99%2017th%20Century%20Haveli%20Offers%20200-YO%20Recipes%2C%20Jawai%20Leopard%20Trails%20%26amp%3B%20Village%20Walks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20a%20kid%2C%20one%20of%20the%20stories%20my%20imagination%20would%20create%20was%20one%20where%20I%20would%20become%20a%20princess.%20While%20I%20grew%20up%20watching%20European%20princesses%20in%20their%20beautiful%20gowns%2C%20there%20was%20something%20about%20the%20idea%20of%20an