h%20is%20a%20five-hour%20drive%20away%20from%20Jaipur%2C%C2%A0%20date%20back%20to%20the%2017th%20century%20when%20Paramveer%E2%80%99s%20ancestors%20ruled%20the%20land.%20Running%20the%20place%20with%20his%20brother%2C%20Bhanwar%20Veer%20Vinod%20Singh%2C%20he%20recounts%20his%20initial%20idea%20of%20setting%20up%20the%20place.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20to%20convert%20our%20ancestral%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F349510%2Fkalimpong-homestay-vacation-palighar-ahana-kabir-gurung-duo-terrace-gardening-composting-activity-treks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehome%20into%20a%20homestay%3C%2Fa%3E%20hotel%20came%20to%20me%20while%20I%20was%20pursuing%20my%20post-graduation%20in%20pharmaceuticals%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20working%20in%20pharmaceutical%20research%20and%20development.%20Despite%20having%20a%20science%20background%20with%20no%20prior%20experience%20in%20hospitality%2C%20I%20harboured%20a%20dream%20to%20create%20a%20homestay%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-12-1717768120.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rawla%20Bisalpur%20Homestay%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-12-1717768120.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-12-1717768120-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-12-1717768120-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-12-1717768120-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-12-1717768120-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352425%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERawla%20Bisalpur%20Homestay%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20decided%20to%20move%20closer%20to%20home%20and%20start%20convincing%20their%20parents.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20elder%20brother%2C%20an%20engineer%2C%20and%20I%20faced%20significant%20challenges%20convincing%20our%20parents.%20They%20were%20sceptical%20and%20worried%20that%20I%20was%20too%20young%20and%20that%20leaving%20a%20stable%20job%20would%20waste%20both%20time%20and%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20scepticism%20was%20also%20rooted%20in%20the%20belief%20that%20only%20large%20properties%2C%20like%20the%20grand%20%3Cem%3Ehavelis%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20Jaipur%20with%2050%20or%20100%20rooms%2C%20could%20attract%20guests.%20However%2C%20I%20was%20convinced%20that%20a%20smaller%2C%20more%20intimate%20setting%20would%20work%20just%20as%20well.%20After%20persistent%20persuasion%2C%20my%20father%20finally%20agreed%20during%20Diwali%20in%202017%2C%20offering%20to%20finance%20the%20project%20while%20leaving%20the%20execution%20up%20to%20me.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20several%20years%2C%20they%20remained%20deeply%20involved%20in%20the%20project%2C%20networking%20with%20individuals%20in%20the%20travel%20industry%20and%20inviting%20experts%20to%20provide%20feedback.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20began%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335727%2Fintach-bengaluru-convenor-meera-iyer-restoring-forgotten-heritage-conservation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erestoration%20process%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20in%202019%2C%20we%20proudly%20opened%20our%20homestay%2C%20blending%20our%20rich%20heritage%20with%20modern%20hospitality%2C%20allowing%20visitors%20to%20experience%20the%20charm%20and%20history%20of%20our%20ancestral%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20restoration%2C%20the%20duo%20decided%20to%20maintain%20the%20original%20structure%20while%20enhancing%20the%20ground%20floor%2C%20which%20was%20previously%20unused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20family%20continued%20living%20on%20the%20first%20floor%2C%20keeping%20our%20personal%20and%20guest%20spaces%20separate.%20The%20restoration%20aimed%20to%20preserve%20the%20original%20architecture%2C%20using%20local%20artisans%20without%20involving%20any%20architects%2C%20engineers%2C%20or%20designers%20due%20to%20the%20small%20and%20remote%20location%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20front%20fa%C3%A7ade%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehaveli%3C%2Fem%3E%20resembles%20a%20mud%20castle%20built%20from%20lime%2C%20mud%2C%20and%20bricks%20without%20any%20stonework.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20traditional%20construction%20method%20has%20a%20natural%20temperature-regulating%20effect%2C%20keeping%20the%20interiors%20warm%20in%20winter%20and%20cool%20in%20summer.%20We%20focused%20on%20restoring%20the%20flooring%20and%20ensuring%20the%20guests%E2%80%99%20comfort%20while%20preserving%20the%20historical%20essence%20of%20the%20place.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20problems%20he%20faced%20during%20the%20restoration%20work%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CRemoving%20the%20original%20big%20stones%20from%20the%20flooring%20was%20a%20difficult%20task.%20Additionally%2C%20restoring%20the%20area%20that%20used%20to%20serve%20as%20stables%20was%20particularly%20challenging%20due%20to%20its%20location%20at%20the%20base%20of%20a%20hill%2C%20which%20caused%20rainwater%20to%20flow%20naturally%20into%20the%20structure.%20We%20needed%20to%20restore%20the%20flooring%20in%20this%20area%20as%20well%2C%20ensuring%20it%20remained%20true%20to%20the%20original%20construction%20methods.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-v